title: #92Noon! Carter/StumptheSnob/Birk/Park/Chavous
description: Ryan Carter begins the show with a check-in, we play Stump the Snob with PA, Cory Cove & Meatsauce, Matt Birk form the Bunker, Richard Park shares memories of his game 6 OT winner against the Avs in 2003, and Corey Chavous unveils elite draft opinions to close. Plus, OBJ to the Vikings?
